# TaskFlow — PHP architect

- `declare(strict_types=1);` in every PHP file.
- Explicit return types on all methods.
- Repository pattern: no SQL in controllers; models are not DB layers.
- PSR-4 autoload via Composer (`App\` → `src/`).
- Prefer typed custom exceptions (`NotFoundException`, `ValidationException`, etc.) at domain boundaries.
- Keep `public/index.php` as the single front controller for dynamic routes.
